Description: Fit computational and measurement models using full Bayesian inference. 
    The package provides a simple and accessible interface by translating complex
    domain-specific models into 'brms' syntax, a powerful and flexible framework for
    fitting Bayesian regression models using 'Stan'. The package is designed so that
    users can easily apply state-of-the-art models in various research fields, and so
    that researchers can use it as a new model development framework.
